title: Charley Harper Cool Cardinals Holiday Cards
description:
Of all of Charley Harper’s beloved creatures, his cardinal may be the most popular. Here are four renditions certain to put you in the holiday spirit. Contains five cards of each of the following works: Adaptation of Cool Cardinal Adaptation of Charley’s Cardinal Coniferous Cardinal B-r-r-r-r-rdbath
  • Dimensions: Box size 5.4 x 7.4 x 1.5 in. Card size 5 x 7 in.
  • Materials: Recycled paper with soy-based inks, high-quality 250 gsm card stock, soft white envelopes
  • Inside message: Season’s Greetings
